OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777986670
OL,3,CTwo primary school sisters fundraise
OL,4,Cfor deaf charities
OL,6,FGabriel Morris met the two sisters in
OL,7,FWorkington.
OL,9,FTwo sisters who were both born with
OL,10,Fprofound deafness have been
OL,11,Ffundraising for causes close to their
OL,12,Fhearts.
OL,14,FViolet and Fearne Murray, who are 6
OL,15,Fand 9-years-old respectively, walked,
OL,16,Fran, scootered or cycled every day
OL,17,Fduring April, to raise money for the
OL,18,FJames Cook Hospital in Middlesbrough,
OL,19,Fwhere they were both fitted with
OL,20,Fcochlear implants.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
