PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777986670
OL,3,CTwo primary school sisters fundraise
OL,4,Cfor deaf charities
OL,6,FThe girls, who hail from Workington,
OL,7,Fare also fundraising for the National
OL,8,FDeaf Children's Society.
OL,10,FFearne said: "It took ages to hear
OL,11,Fproperly, so you have a special
OL,12,Foperation to help you."
OL,14,FWhen asked if all their walking and
OL,15,Fcycling was hard work, Violet replied:
OL,16,F"Yes!"
OL,18,FHer elder sister corrected her,
OL,19,Fhowever, and said: "No, it's not
OL,20,FViolet, silly!"
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777986670
OL,3,CTwo primary school sisters fundraise
OL,4,Cfor deaf charities
OL,6,FThe girls' father, Alan Murray, said:
OL,7,F"They've done this challenge to show
OL,8,Fthat deafness should be embraced. That
OL,9,Fbasically, hearing loss is nothing out
OL,10,Fof the ordinary.
OL,12,F"There's going to be more and more
OL,13,Fchildren with hearing impairments.
OL,15,F"We want to get across that slogan,
OL,16,Fthat 'deaf kids rock'."
OL,18,FThe sisters are also learning British
OL,19,FSign Language, to help them
OL,20,Fcommunicate at night.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
