PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777986670
OL,3,CTwo primary school sisters fundraise
OL,4,Cfor deaf charities
OL,6,FThe implants must charge overnight, so
OL,7,Fthis is how they speak to each other
OL,8,Fwhile their batteries are replenished.
OL,10,FDuring the day, however, the girls
OL,11,Fboth attend a mainstream school.
OL,13,FWhat are cochlear implants?
OL,15,FA cochlear implant is an electronic
OL,16,Fhearing device, which is implanted
OL,17,Finto the ear through surgery.
OL,19,FThe device is used for people with
OL,20,Fsevere to profound hearing loss, where
OL,21,Fhearing aids would not suffice.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
