FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777986670
OL,3,CTwo primary school sisters fundraise
OL,4,Cfor deaf charities
OL,6,FUnlike a hearing aid, which makes
OL,7,Fsounds louder, a cochlear implant
OL,8,Fturns sound into electric signals. It
OL,9,Fsends these signals directly to the
OL,10,Fhearing nerve, which passes them onto
OL,11,Fthe brain.
OL,13,FCochlear implants do not restore
OL,14,Fhearing entirely, and results can vary
OL,15,Fin people.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
